Example

  library(rhpgl)
  hpgl('/tmp/iris.hpgl')
  plot(iris)
  dev.off()

View the file with hp2xx

  hp2xx /tmp/iris.hpgl

Helpful help

* http://cran.r-project.org/doc/manuals/r-release/R-ints.html

svglite, as an example of something similar

    git clone git@github.com:hadley/svglite.git
    git checkout 891aca3a0340e097be1cdefb7e347263ff72a84d

grDevices source code, as an example of something more complicated

